Interface SelectableMappings

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    EmbeddableMappingType, NonAggregatedIdentifierMapping.IdentifierValueMapper
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractEmbeddableMapping, EmbeddableMappingTypeImpl, IdClassEmbeddable, SelectableMappingsImpl, SingleSelectableMappings, VirtualIdEmbeddable
    public interface SelectableMappings
    A container for multiple selectable (column, formula) mappings.
